name: SUNNYSIDE EGG SHAPER
description:
The Sunnyside egg shaper is sure to brighten up even the most miserable day! 

Go on, shine some light onto your breakfast table with this silicon shaper that will make your plate a work of art! 

It really is the cutest way to eat an egg! 

Easy to use and comes with instructions.

name: UNICORN SPRINKLES SHAKER
description:
Decorating your cupcakes can now be a truly magical experience with this wondrous unicorn shaker. 

Simply fill this marvelous creature with delicious goodies and then dust any delicious treat to your hearts content. 

The unicorn sprinkles shaker is a MUST for your kitchen. Baking appliances in the shape of mythical creatures don't come much better than this!

Dimensions: 10cm long x 9cm long approx

Made from plastic. Easily washable

name: CHRISTMAS SUNGLASSES
description:
Move over Dame Edna! 

These awesome sunglasses are the most fashionable way to shield your eyes from all the bling Santa has in store for you on Christmas Day!

name: ROY LICHTENSTEIN 2014 CALENDAR
description:
This beautiful calendar features twelve of Lichtenstein's most iconic works.

30cm x 30cm

name: BUNNY SUICIDES 2014 CALENDAR
description:
The dark comic appeal of the Bunny Suicides is back for 2014 with this fantastic calendar. Cartoonist Andy Riley’s miserable bunnies have devised a whole new collection of morbid schemes to end their hopeless little lives.

30cm x 30cm

name: KEITH HARING 2014 CALENDAR
description:
Keith Haring was one of the Twentieth Century's most iconic artists and this lovely calendar features twelve of his classic works.

30cm x 30cm

name: KITSCH 2014 CALENDAR
description:
This fun 2014 calendar unashamedly celebrates all things Kitsch. From toilet roll covers to flamingos, Cuckoo Clocks to gnomes... there is a fabulous picture of a Kitsch item to go with every month of the year.


30cm x 30cm

name: BUNNY SUICIDES 2014 DIARY
description:
This delightful engagement format diary features the darkly comic Bunny Suicides drawings by Andy Riley. 

The diary features a week to view format and has 12 Bunny Suicide illustrations scattered throughout. 

The diary is spiral bound with a plastic cover and back which will ensure the diary is protected when it's in your bag! 

Dimensions: 18cm x 22cm x 0.5cm approx

52 pages

name: COLOUR ME SWOOOOON
description:
COLOUR ME SWOOOOON is the colouring book that's guaranteed to make you weak at the knees and squeal with delight! 

There are 128 awesome pages of famous hunks for you to colour in and swoon over; Ryan Gosling, George Clooney, Brad Pitt, One Direction... these are but a few of the handsome males who are waiting for you to get your felt tips all over them! 

As well as all these attractive males for you to colour in there are also lots of fun activities to go with; crosswords, anagrams, quizzes. 

Dimensions: 20cm x 20cm

name: RYAN GOSLING PAPER BOY
description:
After the astonishing success of last year's Ryan Gosling colouring book author and publisher Mel Simone Elliot is back with a Ryan Gosling paper doll book! 

This fabulous Ryan Gosling paper doll book features a nearly naked Ryan for you to dress up in outfits from all the best Ryan Gosling films including The Notebook, Crazy Stupid Love, Drive, The Place Beyond the Pines, Lars and the Real Girl and Blue Valentine. 

As if that wasn't enough there is even a cut out of "George" , Ryan's beloved dog too! 

24 pages

Dimensions: 30cm x 21cm

name: RYAN GOSLING COLOURING IN BOOK
description:
The hottest Colouring in book of all time has to be the Ryan Gosling colouring book! 

This fantastically fun colouring in book from I LOVE MEL is dedicated to Hollywood's hunk du jour Ryan Gosling! There are 15 pages of Ryan for you to get busy with!

Dimensions: 20.6 x 20.4 x 0.8 cm

name: HEY GIRL - RYAN GOSLING TEA TOWEL
description:
This tea towel is going to DRIVE you crazy! Ryan Gosling really does want to help you do your dishes! 

The Ryan Gosling tea towel features three handsome Ryan Goslings; Classic Ryan Gosling; Gosling the hipster; and Ryan "the charmer" Gosling. 

This fantastic Ryan Gosling tea towel is designed by New Zealand based illustrator Dear Colleen. 

Dimensions: 48cm x 76cm 
Material: 100% cotton

name: PUGS NOT DRUGS TEA TOWEL
description:
The perfect tea towel for clean living canine lovers! 

The fabulous PUGS NOT DRUGS tea towel is designed by Gemma Correll. 

Dimensions: 76 x 48cm

100% Cotton

name: LEMONS TEA TOWEL
description:
We just love the design of this cute tea towel. 

New Zealand based illustrator Dear Colleen has created this lovely design. We think "when life hands you lemons make a gin and tonic" is very good advice indeed! 

Dimensions: 52cm x 77cm

100% cotton

name: HOLLYWOOD DISHES TEA TOWEL
description:
This wonderful tea towel deserves an Oscar and a star on the Hollywood walk of fame! 

The Hollywood Dishes tea towel features five of Hollywood's hottest male stars; Johhny Depp, Owen Wilson, Brad Pitt, Jake Gyllenhall and George Clooney! 

The Hollywood Dishes tea towel is designed by New Zealand based illustrator Dear Colleen and above each cute portrait of these leading men is a fun phrase about them. For example above Owen Wilson it says "aka ... the butterscotch stallion"!

Dimensions: 48cm x 76cm 

100% cotton

name: COSTUME DRAMA TEA TOWEL
description:
A tea towel for Jane Austen fans and fans of hunky men in period costume too! The costume drama tea towel features three hunks who's names are synonymous with costume drama; Colin Firth, Hugh Grant and Sean Bean! 

This fabulous tea towel is sure to you swoon! The costume drama tea towel is designed by New Zealand based illustrator Dear Colleen. 

Dimensions: 48cm x 76cm 

100% cotton

name: SMILEY LAMP
description:
The Smiley lamp is the newest addition to the wonderful lighting designs of Dutch design duo MR MARIA. 

The Smiley lamp is certain to put a smile on your face and will brighten up any room you choose to put it in. 

In an exclusive collaboration between Mr Maria and Smiley Company, the trademark holder, Mr Maria has created an exclusive never seen before lamp of the legendary Smiley. 

The Smiley Happy Decor XL  lamp has a bright dimmable LED lamp which gives the Smiley lamp a beautiful warm glow and lights up every room.

Specifications

Material: Polyethylene

Dimensions: 43.5cm Diameter

Weight: 3kg

Lamp type: LED

name: KOKESHI LAMP
description:
KOKESHI LAMP
(Japanese Doll lamp)

This fabulous “kokeshi” lamp is based on the distinctive silhouette of the Japanese Kokeshi doll. In Japan the Kokeshi doll is seen as a good luck charm and some even think the doll helps to ward off evil spirits. 

Now the Kokeshi has become a wonderful lamp, designed by Dutch designers MR MARIA!

Dimensions: L x W x H = 36cm x 33cm x 63cm

Material: Polyethylene

LED LAMP (25,000 light hours)

5 step Dimmer switch

name: NANUK - POLAR BEAR LIGHT
description:
A beautiful light that looks like a little polar bear cub, designed by Dutch designers MR MARIA. 

This light is sure to melt even the most icy heart!

Dimensions: LxWxH = 35cm x 35cm x 41cm

Material: Polyethylene

LED LAMP  (25,000 light hours)

5 step dimmer switch

name: ANANA  - BABY ELEPHANT LIGHT
description:
A very beautiful statement light inspired by the cute features of a baby elephant, designed by Dutch designers MR MARIA

The light is called Anana and emits a soft comforting glow. Suitable for adults and children alike! 

Dimensions: LxWxH = 43cm x 43cm x 51cm

Material: Polyethylene

LED LAMP  (25,000 light hours)

Dimmer switch with five brightness setting

name: GIANT MIFFY LIGHT
description:
In 1955 by Dutch artist Dick Bruna created Miffy after telling his son stories about a rabbit they seen on a beach holiday. Since then Miffy's adventures have spanned more than 30 books and have taken her to the zoo, the seaside, an art gallery and many other locations.

Over 50 years later Miffy's future is even brighter because she is now a tremendously appealing light! This light is made from polyethelene which is virtually unbreakable and can also be recycled without harm to the environment.

The light is made and designed in Holland by Dutch designers MR MARIA and is an officially licensed Miffy product.

This is the GIANT version of the light which is 80cm high x 40cm wide! There is a smaller version available which is 50cm high.

Dimensions: L x W x H = 40cm x 40cm x 80cm

Material: Polyethylene

LED LAMP (25,000 light hours)

5 step Dimmer switch

name: MIFFY LIGHT
description:
In 1955 by Dutch artist Dick Bruna created Miffy (or nijntie in Dutch) after telling his son stories about a rabbit they seen on a beach holiday. Since then Miffy's adventures have spanned more than 30 books and have taken her to the zoo, the seaside, an art gallery and many other locations.

The light is made and designed in Holland by Dutch designers MR MARIA and is an officially licensed Miffy product. 

This is the small version of the Miffy light. There is also a larger model (80cm) available. 

Dimensions: L x W x H = 25cm x 25cm x 50cm

Material: Polyethylene

LED LAMP (25,000 light hours)

5 step Dimmer switch

description:
This gummy bear night light is simply awesome. 

The night light is modelled on the instantly recognisable features of the gummy bear which we all fondly remember from many years ago! 

Gently squeeze the gummy bear's tummy to switch on the comforting LED light source inside. Squeeze the bear's tummy again to turn the light off. The gummy bear night light also has a handy timer switch which if activated will ensure that the light goes out after one hour. 

Dimensions: 18 x 8.5cm

Requires two AA batteries (not included)

Also available in green and yellow

name: RABBIT LAMP
description:
This lovely white rabbit lamp is made from bone china in England. 

Once switched on the light inside shines through the china giving off a warm comforting glow. 

The rabbit lamp is perfect for babies and children as a night light, but is also well loved by adults too!

Made in England

Dimensions: 22cm high

Comes in a gift box 

Bulb supplied

name: OWL LAMP
description:
This beautiful bone china owl lamp is made from fine bone china and glows from the inside. 

The owl lamp is the perfect gift for a child or for any owl loving adult. The owl lamp will look amazing in any room of your home!


Made in England 

Dimensions: 22cm high

Comes in a lovely gift box

Bulb included

name: CAT LAMP
description:
CAT LAMP

This beautiful cat lamp is made from fine bone china. 

The cat lamp is very elegant and has a rather art deco shape and style. 

Made in England

Dimensions: 33cm long 12cm high

Comes with gift box

Bulb included

name: RABBIT NIGHT LIGHT
description:
This super cute white rabbit shaped night light is sure to brighten up your world!

The rabbit LED night light has an on/off switch and batteries are included. 

Requires 3 button batteries LR44 (included)

Dimensions: 15cm high

name: WHITE RABBIT LAMP
description:
This wondrous lamp is modelled on the gorgeous features of a white rabbit. 

Sure to brighten up any room and make everyone a happy bunny! This white rabbit lamp is a must have

Dimensions:  26cm x 17cm approx

The white rabbit lamp is supplied with bulb and British plug. Ready to plug in and go once you receive it. 

15 watt bulb

name: BOOKREST LAMP
description:
This bedside bookrest lamp is a real gem. Whether you're partial to taking a Jackie Collins to bed or dozing off to Kafka this bookrest lamp is a must for all you bookworms out there. 

You'll never need worry about losing your page again since you can simply place the open book on top of the bookrest lamp, ready for when you want to pick it up again. Also, once the book is atop the lamp it becomes a cute little house. 

Materials: Frosted glass
Dimensions: 115 x 150 x 145mm

Comes packaged with energy saving 11w bulb and flex with UK plug.

name: TINY TIM BOOKLIGHT
description:
This Tiny Tim booklight is a very fetching miniature articulated lamp that puts light just where you need it. 

The Tiny Tim booklight is 13cm high and can be attached to your book or placed near a laptop or wherever you may be working and in need of some extra light. 

The Tiny Tim booklight has a powerful LED bulb and is battery-powered. It comes complete with a miniature on-off switch too!

name: BLACK KIT CAT CLOCK
description:
The charming Kit Cat Clock was invented in 1932 in a small town in Oregon.  The wagging tail and rolling eyes of this friendly feline clock make it a real delight! 

The black and white version of the Kit Kat clock is the original design, but there are now other colours too! 

--- 
The kit cat clock has moving eyes and the tail wags too. 

Powered by 2  x C Batteries (not included)

Dimensions: 40cm x 10cm x 6cm approx

name: CREAM KIT CAT CLOCK
description:
The charming cream Kit Cat Clock was invented in 1932 in a small town in Oregon. The wagging tail and rolling eyes of this friendly feline clock make it a real delight!

This cream Kit Cat Clock is a limited edition. 

---
The Kit Cat clock has moving eyes and the tail wags too.

Powered by 2 x C Batteries (not included)

Dimensions: 40cm x 10cm x 6cm approx

The Kit Cat Clock is also available in other colours

name: HERE KITTY DOORSTOP
description:
The HERE KITTY doorstop is simply the PURRfect way to hold your door open! 

This super cute double sided doorstop is modelled on a cute cat's paw! Who knew that a doorstop could be this cute?!

Now you can hold your door open so your kitty cat can come and go as they please! Which is great since we all know that cats can never make up their minds!

The Here Kitty doorstop is the perfect doorstop for any home whether you have cats or not!

100% silicone

Dimensions: 10cm long approx

name: SPARROW KEYRING
description:
This cute product is both a keyring and a house for your keys. 

The house can be hung on a wall using screws or with the sticky pads provided. Once hung on the wall the house is a home for your keys ensuring that they never get lost! 

The sparrow keyring also doubles as a whistle.

name: SHOWGIRLS AND SHELL NECKLACE
description:
This is some seriously adorable BLING! 

This statement necklace is a real cracker! Made from gold plated brass and enamel.

Each showgirl measures 7cm from head to toe.

Clam shell measures 4cm tall.

Total length, including chain, is 60cm.

name: CIRCUS NECKLACE
description:
This stunning necklace is made from gold-plated, enamelled metal on a gold-coloured chain. It depicts two circus gymnasts in flight. 

Each Gymnast measures approximately 11cm toe to toe. 

Designed by Karen Mabon for Red Brick North

name: SWIMMER NECKLACE
description:
This necklace featuring a lovely looking swimmer is the perfect poolside fashion statement. 

This wonderful necklace is made from gold-plated, enamelled metal on a gold-coloured chain.

The diameter of the ring is 4cm and the swimmer is 11cm long. The total length of the chain (plus ring and swimmer) is 55cm approx. 

Designed by Karen Mabon for Red Brick North

name: CIRCUS GYMNAST SILK SCARF
description:
This beautiful silk scarf features a charming design of vintage inspired lady circus gymnasts resplendent in their spots and stripes. 

A truly beautiful silk scarf! 

Dimensions: 150cm x 30cm

Designed by Karen Mabon for Red Brick North

name: SWIMMING POOL SCARF
description:
The perfect poolside fashion statement!

This stunning silk scarf features a wonderful aquatic design of ladies swimming and diving. 

100% Silk

Dimensions: 135cm x 23cm

name: BLACK FOREST SILK SCARF
description:
A fabulous silk scarf!

This gorgeous silk scarf features a striking design of long distance runners streaming through a mythical black forest landscape.

Trees, foxes and pair of swans also feature as part of the designs.

Approx. 150cm x 30cm

Digitally Printed 100% Silk Twill

Designed by Karen Mabon for Red Brick North

name: KEITH HARING DANCING PEOPLE WALL STICKERS
description:
Make a room instantly hip with these bold Keith Haring wall stickers.

This pack contains 5 classic Keith Haring dancing people measuring 30cm approximately. They can be arranged in your chosen formation.

Pack comes with full instructions for installation.

Pack measurements: 70cm x 50cm

name: KEITH HARING DANCERS AND HEART WALL STICKERS
description:
Make a room instantly hip with these bold Keith Haring wall stickers. 

These lovely wall stickers feature classic Haring characters and a classic Haring heart. 

This pack contains 10 dancing people measuring 30cm approximately and a heart measuring 10cm approximately. They can be arranged in your chosen formation.

Pack comes with full instructions for installation. 

Pack measurements: 70cm x 50cm

name: KEITH HARING DANCING DOGS WALL STICKERS
description:
Make a room instantly hip with these bold Keith Haring wall stickers. 

This pack contains 6 dancing dogs measuring 30cm approximately. They can be arranged in your chosen formation. 

Pack comes with full instructions for installation. 

Pack measurements: 70cm x 50cm

name: BABUSHKUPS
description:
This delightful set of three nesting glass tumblers is super cute!

Each glass features a different Babushka (or Matryoshka as they say in Russia!) doll design. 

This set of Babushka glasses will also save shelf space because they can be stacked inside one another exactly like real Russian Dolls! 

Each set of BABUSHKUPS contains three glass tumblers (8,10 and 14 fluid ounce capacity). The tumblers are made from durable hand-blown borosilicate glass. 

Hand Wash Only

For Adult use only

name: SNACK & STACK
description:
The snack & stack cutlery set contains a knife, fork and spoon each with a different coloured lego like silicone handle. These mid size utensils are perfect for adults and children alike! 

The building block nature of the brightly coloured handles means that they can be stacked on top of each other too! 

Perfect for brightening up your lunch box or picnic basket! 

Packaging dimensions: 16cm x 8cm x 2.5cm approx

name: MOOD LIGHTING
description:
Lighten up! It's time to inject some personality into your boring light switches with this fantastic pack of mood lighting stickers which you can use on your light switches to create up to sixteen different faces. 

The stickers are very easy to put on and even easier to peel off. 

The Mood Lighting pack contains twelve sheets of stickers. Enough to make sixteen different faces.

name: DAVID BOWIE MASK
description:
Become an icon with this amazing mask!

This fantastic David Bowie mask enables you to become the iconic singer and live out your rock star dreams!

Buy this David Bowie mask and find out what life on Mars is really like!

Dimensions: 25cm x 20cm

name: DAVID BOWIE PAPER DOLLS BOOK
description:
GROUND CONTROL TO MAJOR TOM... HAVE YOU SEEN THIS DAVID BOWIE PAPER DOLL BOOK?!


The Thin White Duke, Ziggy Stardust, Aladdin Sane, The goblin King from Labyrinth... David Bowie has had so many different fabulous incarnations over the years we get exhausted just trying to remember them! 

Now you can have your very own David Bowie paper dolls! 

This WONDERFUL David Bowie paper doll book from I LOVE MEL is fabulous and features loads of different outfits that you dress up Mr Bowie in!   

Dimensions: 30cm x 20cm

name: RIHANNA PAPER DOLL BOOK
description:
Who's that chick?! 

It's Rihanna , but this time she's shining bright like a diamond and made entirely of paper! 

This awesome paper doll by I LOVE MEL features two Rihanna paper dolls for you to cut out and dress up in variety of 15 fabulous outfits. It's the most fun you'll ever have with a pair of scissors!

24 pages

Dimensions: 30.5 x 25.4 x 0.5 cm

name: DEBBIE HARRY PAPER DOLL BOOK
description:
You'd have to have a heart of glass not to love this awesome Debbie Harry paper doll book! 

This book contains two Deborah Harry dolls and lots of different outfits to cut out and dress them up in. 


Dimensions: 30cm x 20cm

Illustrated and published by I LOVE MEL

name: ADELE PAPER DOLL BOOK
description:
This lovely Adele paper doll book features two paper dolls of Britain's latest chart topper. Put on your ADELE CD and spend a while carefully cutting out the Adele dolls and their accompanying outfits (we counted 17 of them). 

Comes with full instructions too!


Dimensions: 30cm x 20cm

name: CARA DELEVINGNE COLOURING BOOK
description:
Yes, that's right! Colour Me Good Cara is actually a whole colouring book dedicated to super duper super model of the moment Cara Delevingne! 

There are a whole sixteen different images of Miss Delevingne for you to colour in! 

Cara is seen doing lots of different fashiony things; getting made up for a shoot, pulling a funny face for the paps and just generally being beautifully cool and awesome!

Colour Me Good Cara is the colouring book of the season! Don't be seen with anything else!

name: COLOUR ME GOOD - GINGER
description:
In the bad old days it wasn't necessarily "cool" to be a ginger (or a "red-head" as they say in America). 

But  that's all changed because now there is even a whole colouring book devoted to ginger people! 

This fabulous colouring book by I LOVE MEL features sixteen different World famous red heads for you to colour in! 

Nicole Kidman, Damian Lewis, Rupert Grint, Molly Ringwold, Prince Harry and Julianne Moore are all featured alongside many other World famous ginger people! 

24 Pages

Dimensions: 21 x 21 cm

name: 1980s COLOURING IN BOOK
description:
This 1980s colouring book from I LOVE MEL showcases everything great and fun from the 80s! Alexis Carrington,  Gordon the Gopher, roller boots, Madonna, BMX bikes.... they're all featured in this unashamedly retro publication! Dozens of 80s icons for you to colour in!

Dimensions: 21cm x 21cm

name: RECORD SLEEVES COLOURING IN BOOK
description:
This colouring in book is BAD - but in a good way! 

This gorgeous colouring in book contains dozens of classic album covers for you to colour in. There's Blur, Bowie, Jacko, Britney, Kylie, Bruce Springsteen and loads more! 

Grab your felt tips and ROCK OUT!

Dimensions 21cm x 21cm

32 pages

name: 1990s COLOURING IN BOOK
description:
It seems like only yesterday that John Major (remember him?) was Prime Minister, The Spice Girls were topping the charts and we all started getting mobile phones. 

Well now you can relive the 90s with this fabulous 1990s colouring in book. Loads of 90s favourites are featured and are just begging for you to work your magic on them as soon as your can grab a felt tip pen! There are 18 designs in all! That's loads!

Dimensions: 21cm x 21cm

name: HORROR FILM COLOURING IN BOOK
description:
COLOUR ME GOOD "ARRGGGHHHH" is the scariest in the series of fabulous colouring in books from I LOVE MEL. 

The book is a visual feast for film buffs featuring scenes and characters from classic horror films. Carrie, The Shining, Psycho, Jaws (or to be really pernickity Jaws 2) are all featured. There are 18 different images to colour in!

Everyone will want to have a "stab" at colouring these wicked images in!! 

Colour Me Good - Arrggghhhh is a must for all scary movie fans!! 

Dimensions: 21cm x 21cm

name: OFF THE HOOK SHOWER HEAD
description:
Forget taking a cold shower; now you can take a "cool" shower with this this retro phone inspired shower head!

The "off the hook" shower head has a universal fitting which fits all standard shower hoses. This fabulous shower head is easy to install and very easy to clean too! 

Dimensions: 25cm x 6.6cm x 6.1cm

Made from ABS Plastic

name: SOCIAL MEDIA SHOWER CURTAIN
description:
For the many millions of us with a chronic social media addiction only this shower curtain will do! 

This hilarious plastic curtain has been printed like the timeline page for our favourite social network and there is even a clear box in the corner for you to show your face! 

Hilarious! 

Dimensions: 180cm x 180cm approx

name: SCRABBLE COASTERS
description:
You won't be lost for words with these Scrabble drinks coasters!

54 Pub style cardboard coasters. 

Includes two full alphabet sets and blanks.

Printed on both sides. Reverse side of coasters feature: Triple Word Score, Double Word Score, Triple Letter Score, Double Letter Score, Scrabble Star

The coasters are packaged in a nice metal tin with a Scrabble design on it.

Dimensions: 10 x 10 x 7cm (tin)

name: SCRABBLE FRIDGE MAGNETS
description:
Increase your literacy every time you open your fridge with these wonderful Scrabble fridge magnets!

Each pack of Scrabble fridge magnets contains over 100 magnets featuring not only the Scrabble alphabet letters and other Scrabble favourites such as Double and Triple Word Scores, Double and Triple Letter scores and the Scrabble star. 

The magnets are a wood effect design. 

Dimensions: Each magnet measures 2cm x 2cm

name: MUFFIN TOPS
description:
This set of four cupcake moulds is pretty darn funny! 

Each of the silicone cupcake moulds is designed to look like a pair of jeans. Simply fill each mould with your favourite cake batter, pop them in the oven and that familiar little (or not so little) bulge will develop! 

Each set of Muffin Tops is packaged in a delightful presentation box making it the perfect gift for a muffin loving friend (or for your muffin loving self!). The box even contains handy baking hints, so that you can make your muffins even tastier! 

Made from food grade silicone rubber

Dimensions: each mould is 5cm x 5cm

name: GIN AND TITONIC
description:
Of all the novelty ice trays out there this Gin and Titonic ice tray has to be one of the best! 

Each pack of gin and titonic contains 4 ocean liners and 4 icebergs. 

Dimensions: 15cm x 16cm approx

name: MR ROMANO CHEESE GRATER
description:
Whoever said a cheese grater could not cute clearly spoke before seeing this delightful fellow! 

Mr Romano is a cheese grater which looks like a friendly bearded old man! 

As the packaging says "Invite a grate guy to dinner" 

Mr. Romano is molded from a high-tech engineering plastic that is food-safe, dishwasher-safe and highly durable.

Dimensions: 18cm long x 9cm wide

name: THE OBSESSIVE CHEF CHOPPING BOARD
description:
This is the only chopping board out there for all you crazily obsessive chefs. Monica Geller would love this!!

The Beachwood chopping board is etched with precise measurements and angles to guide your knife and ensure you chop your ingredients to exactly the right size and shape!
 
The obsessive chef chopping board is made from strong, hard-wearing Beechwood which is naturally anti-bacterial. Plus it’s naturally anti-bacterial! (oh! We already said that!)

Hand wash only

Dimensions: 29cm(L) x 23cm(W) x 1.5cm(D)

It's heavy so postage is quite a bit especially to foreign destinations!

name: GAY BAR SOAP
description:
Whoever said a bar of soap couldn't be funny was wrong! 

This hilarious pink bar of (rose scented) soap has the words GAY BAR embossed on it. 

The Gay Bar soap is good clean fun for all people of all persuasions! 

Dimensions: 8cm long approx

name: BICYCLE RIDER'S LUNCH BOX
description:
This cute retro style lunch box is the perfect gift for any of your bicycle riding friends or loved ones. The air tight lid will keep your lunch fresh as you pedal about! 

There is a lovely design on the lid of the lunch box featuring a bicycle and the inspirational wording "fortitude, endurance and invigoration" 

The lunch box is made from hard wearing plastic and is dishwasher safe. 

Dimensions:  15 cm x 14 cm x 7 cm

name: BICYCLE MUG
description:
This mug is real classic! 

The 1/2 pint mug is decorated (on both sides) in 24 carat gold with a simple yet stunning design of a bike. 

Dimensions: H 9cm W 9cm

Please wash by hand. Not suitable for microwave use.

Made entirely in Stoke on Trent, England

name: BICYCLE BIBLE
description:
The Bicycle Bible is the perfect gift for any bike obsessed cyclist. 

The Bicycle Bible is a compact, tough notebook designed with the cyclist in mind. 

The cover is made of 100% recycled tyres so there's minimal chance of it getting battered in transit. 

Inside, there are 62 mixed plain and lined pages for you to keep notes. There are also pages of handy information on bicycle maintenance - like how to mend a puncture and keep your bike healthy.

name: 100 POSTCARDS FROM PENGUIN
description: A collection of 100 postcards, each featuring a different and iconic Penguin book jacket. From classics to crime, here are over seventy years of quintessentially British design in one box. In 1935 Allen Lane stood on a platform at Exeter railway station, looking for a good book for the journey to London. His disappointment at the poor range of paperbacks on offer led him to found Penguin Books. The quality paperback had arrived. Declaring that 'good design is no more expensive than bad', Lane was adamant that his Penguin paperbacks should cost no more than a packet of cigarettes, but that they should always look distinctive. Ever since then, from their original – now world-famous – look featuring three bold horizontal stripes, through many different stylish, inventive and iconic cover designs, Penguin’s paperback jackets have been a constantly evolving part of Britain’s culture. And whether they’re for classics, crime, reference or prize-winning novels, they still follow Allen Lane’s original design mantra. Sometimes, you definitely should judge a book by its cover.
